Sharpclaws bolted a metal plate in place, then went to help Starstorm.

Sharpclaw: Almost, O dark freaking one...

Wolfenstein volunteered himself to build the device. As he wasn't very
good at programming, he simply put a use condition restricting use to
Predacons, but he left another one to allow reprogrammation later.

Wolfenstein: Here, it's done. But what about the third reactor?

Dreadplague smiled.

Dread: Clever, aren't you? The last one's gonna be the maximal
reactor. They have to be quick though. Unicron could be here any
moment now...
